title: Barlowe's Guide To Extraterrestrials
description: Introducing extraterrestrials, one man has seen them. Wayne Douglas Barlowe's brilliant portraits bring to life 50 aliens from science fiction literature. Note: Based on existing version at (https://archive.org/details/barlowes-guide-to-extraterrestrials), but with a missing blank page replaced, two duplicate pages removed, and the pages of the fold-out "Comparative Size Chart" reordered.
